sTwTory
    &w&para <b>Vocabulary Paragraph</b>
    &w&para &w&imd Alice’s smile spread across her face&w&semi
    she was <u>elated</u>.
    She’d always been known as an <u>adroit</u> girl, and she used her <u>finesse</u> to escape the party. 
    At the party, she’d found the people to be <u>arcane</u>, and instead of being <u>convivial</u>, the party felt like it was <u>incubating</u> feelings of <u>avarice</u>.
    Everyone was <u>diffused</u> around the room, and they were all <u>maudlin</u> about the objects in the room, which added to the greedy nature of the party.
    The entire event was <u>churlish</u>, which is why Alice was happy to have escaped.
;